{"title":"新路","authors":["陈志铭"],"dates":[{"year":1985,"month":11,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"新路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈志铭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"厦门日报头版：市地名委员会命名四十三条新路。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当楼群象大陆架崛起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲吻广阔的天空，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在楼海的波谷中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新路一条条诞生！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诞生了色彩斑斓的河流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诞生了芬芳馥郁的笑声……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我真想把长眠的奶奶唤醒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扶她走进小“的士”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赏一路树苗抽出嫩绿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看大街橱窗展出画屏。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让女儿坐在自行车上的藤椅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乘“凤凰”逛逛新城，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"道路四通八达不断地伸展！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵，可爱的家乡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新路可是你强健的神经？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我为你感到骄傲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骄傲于更加迷人的青春。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你以崭新的大道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"召唤新世纪叱咤风云。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}